13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 11, Chapter 321, O.S.L.
15 2022 (12 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 1439), is amended to read as
16 follows:
17 Section 1439. The Oklahoma Citizens Participation Act shall not
18 apply to:
19 1. An enforcement action that is brought in the name of this
20 state or a political subdivision of this state by the Attorney
21 General or a district attorney;
22 2. A legal action brought against a person primarily engaged in
23 the business of selling or leasing goods or services, if the
24 statement or conduct the action is based upon arises out of the sale
